data.title: Eugene O'Neill National Historic Site (U.S. National Park Service)
data.text:
Key Figures in Eugene O'Neill's Life and Legacy

Welcome to the "People" section, where you can explore the lives of those who were integral to Eugene O'Neill's journey. From his family and close associates to the influential figures who shaped his career and legacy, including those who continued to be inspired by his work after his death, discover the rich tapestry of relationships that influenced and were influenced by one of America's greatest playwrights.
